room_title: Escape room "Around the World in 60 Minutes" by College Town Escape Rooms in Hattiesburg
review: Amazing experience! The Around the World room is wonderfully designed with clever puzzles and fun, immersive sets. Filled with discovery and surprises around every corner. The staff is enthusiastic and friendly from the moment you arrive to the moment you leave. Can't wait to go back and try the other two rooms!
